<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA21">
<l>tāmuḷarē tammuḷḷa muḷḷuḷatē tāmaraiyiṉ</l>
<l>pūvuḷatē yēttum poḻutuṇṭē – vāmaṉ</l>
<l>ṟirumaruvu tāṇmaruvu ceṉṉiyarē cevvē</l>
<l>yarunarakañ cērva taritu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">I.e., the people who might worship.</note> exist, their minds are inside, there are lotus</l>
<l>flowers, there is time for praising. For those whose heads</l>
<l>connect with the blessed feet of the dwarf,</l>
<l>it is rare that they go straight to harsh hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
